The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm uses histograms computed from hue data, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques for classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
